com.adobe.aem.dermis.model

Interface IProperty

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAsset, ITypeAsset, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IOperationArgument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Property, RestProperty, WSProperty

    public interface IProperty
extends ITypeAsset
    Represents a property and it's metadata description. Property reside within a DataModel and can be used as keys for relationships between DataModel.
